title: Africa Lounge
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Moderate size restaurant with bar, decorated with a safari-esque theme. Located in the A concourse, right across from gate A5. Offers mostly American fare, but advertises as international. Its veggie burger is vegan, comes with chips but you can add fries for $1. Also offers a hummus with pita chips.
